; Regression test for issue #753: prices -A and prices -D doesn't work (BZ#753)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/753
;
; The -A (--average) and -D (--daily) flags don't work properly with the
; prices command. -A shows raw prices instead of a running average.
; -D sums same-day price entries instead of showing the last/average price.

P 2024/01/01 00:00:00 AAPL $100.00
P 2024/01/01 12:00:00 AAPL $110.00
P 2024/01/01 18:00:00 AAPL $120.00
P 2024/01/02 00:00:00 AAPL $130.00

2024/01/01 Buy
    Assets:Investments   1 AAPL @ $100.00
    Assets:Cash

test prices
2024/01/01 AAPL          $100.00
2024/01/01 AAPL          $110.00
2024/01/01 AAPL          $120.00
2024/01/02 AAPL          $130.00
end test

test prices -A
2024/01/01 AAPL          $100.00
2024/01/01 AAPL          $110.00
2024/01/01 AAPL          $120.00
2024/01/02 AAPL          $130.00
end test

test prices -D
2024/01/01 AAPL          $330.00
2024/01/02 AAPL          $130.00
end test
